"tid":1669843,"uid":279356,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T20:41:57.000Z","msg":"應該定立可以每日都做到嘅目標<br />\n養成好習慣<br />\n例如我唔鍾意睇書<br />\n但有某方面嘅知識我想吸收<br />\n就去圖書館度搵target<br />\n將興趣變成習慣之餘又吸收到野<br />\n我嘅興趣係研究精油同DIY美容嘅嘢<br />\n就算我呢一刻冇咁多儲備去買材料<br />\n都可以吸收定一啲新嘅嘢<br />\n等有錢啲嘅時候就可以學以致用<br />\n晚上徹夜難眠嘅時侯<br />\n我會search YouTube做靜觀<br />\n或者聽下啲大自然音效<br />\n會比較快瞓得着"},{"pid":"186c2a94c3c83f0be0202a74266e2f3c4b5e15c7","tid":1669843,"uid":188671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:46:35.000Z","msg":"已經廢咗2定3年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe60a380785ee510fa5cbb7e5f908a84b4a1e3f3","tid":1669843,"uid":282777,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T22:44:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e97c6439a443b1636bb7c294dd74f4a2248a561","tid":1669843,"uid":203662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"186c2a94c3c83f0be0202a74266e2f3c4b5e15c7","tid":1669843,"uid":188671,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:46:35.000Z","msg":"已經廢咗2定3年。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"我同你應該差唔多<br />\n廢左應該都有1年以上<br />\n但你這刻生活快樂嗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d0a9ac5d98608f3067da11e2c2da4e1502aa98","tid":1669843,"uid":86236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"樓主 雖然後生過你小小<br />\n每日都過著咁既生活 係好攰 只能同自己說that's life 其他人都有苦不知<br />\n要相信there must be some way we have not yet thought of"},{"pid":"cdd1ddbafbddf1e0defe08044cc95a3026d7c899","tid":1669843,"uid":203662,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b2d0a9ac5d98608f3067da11e2c2da4e1502aa98","tid":1669843,"uid":86236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T04:26:57.000Z","msg":"樓主 雖然後生過你小小<br />\n每日都過著咁既生活 係好攰 只能同自己說that's life 其他人都有苦不知<br />\n要相信there must be some way we have not y